c3355-5545-418f-8eca-4d9999352ace\">환자의 절반 이상이 과민성 장 증후군 진단을 받고 있습니다!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-be0fda1e-d0d0-4d25-bc08-a313e1cb81f5\"><span style=\"color:#303038;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-df96f8c7-90cf-4ab9-aac7-61272c81ec80\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7f951a93-964c-4d72-a6c3-1d59e3c8fb22\"><span style=\"color:#303038;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-d8815e6f-4634-4457-8b21-e9ee0935c3de\">애꿎은 음식을 탓할 것이 아니라</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c20456ad-0405-408b-93da-7c4dc638a5e2\"><span style=\"color:#303038;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-ab5077df-6af8-456f-a19b-a2225216e92d\">정확한 진단 후 적절한 치료를 받는 것이 중요</span><span style=\"color:#1c1c1c;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-ef193197-b58c-4931-81b4-89e66876ca8b\">한데요~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-10afa9dd-ba1b-41ac-b52f-d03b49e029df\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-94607cb9-ed7f-49a0-9a17-3c7e9927bd82\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line5\" id=\"SE-a5ae63c7-9e7c-4507-80db-cf83357608b2\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line5 se-section-align-left\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-78217817-27d8-4835-bf61-c9a4a789304a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-fbe88960-6845-4c9a-9a5a-a5dec2f9b1af\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-569d829d-7c8d-448d-a01d-ce99b53b6870\">자세한 내용이 궁금하시다면?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-2cf8091c-7c26-4814-922f-bee294b43d59\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-55224004-7a43-4be8-b47c-025d9e0f1f69\">아래의 링크를 클릭해서 칼럼 내용을 확인해주세요 :) </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-c8a6517e-5df0-4719-b5e3-91d5bf8416c4\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-5b5d5971-eaab-4fbe-bcd8-b4bb06a9875f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a80beb7f-cf9c-4e19-8f62-49fb2dc837b3\"><span style=\"color:#303038;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-edc4055a-396c-43e4-b7b0-1a9469312872\"><b>별 이유 없이 반복적으로 속이 안 좋다면 정확한 진단과 치료 필요</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0336cd85-2dec-419f-bf78-700f89f3aaae\"><span style=\"color:#303038;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-c5123a1e-63a0-4e8a-bfa1-b1d135055908\"><b>스트레스, 긴장, 불안 등으로 복통, 설사, 트림, 방귀 증상 나타나</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d0483096-a5d9-45e2-bb44-4f5c60843dbe\"><span style=\"color:#303038;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-1e23192b-2b98-4da4-ad43-6bd2d766ecaf\"><b>증상 완화 위해 ‘식이요법’, ‘운동’, ‘심리적 안정’ 중요</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-792b4dba-cc0c-4683-9059-147f809c51ea\"><span style=\"color:#303038;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-00647a90-4933-45e0-bab6-d8217a6ba92a\"><b>장을 건강하게 하는 ‘한약’, 손으로 치료하는 ‘내장 추나요법’도 도움</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-18585452-cb2e-44eb-bf51-bf7e7e4e93fc\"><span style=\"color:#303038;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-ea6d6531-ae8e-4321-9745-0f6793dfe799\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fd24928d-a0b3-4d52-a5d7-ee49345e744e\"><span style=\"color:#303038;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-a44ec128-359f-47d9-8ea4-7c665655db31\"><a href=\"https://n.news.naver.com/article/011/0004258136?sid&#x3D;103\" class=\"se-link\" target=\"_blank\"><b>https://n.news.naver.com/article/011/0004258136?sid&#x3D;103</b></a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-oglink se-l-large_image\" id=\"SE-23680cf0-98db-4fbe-8d54-34691ab3728d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-oglink se-l-large_image se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-oglink\">\n                                <a href=\"https://n.news.naver.com/article/011/0004258136?sid&#x3D;103\" class=\"se-oglink-thumbnail\" target=\"_blank\">\n                                    <img src=\"https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src&#x3D;%22https%3A%2F%2Fimgnews.pstatic.net%2Fimage%2F011%2F2023%2F11%2F07%2F0004258136_001_20231107091405947.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw800%22&amp;type&#x3D;ff500_300\" class=\"se-oglink-thumbnail-resource\" alt=\"\" />\n                                </a>\n                                <a href=\"https://n.news.naver.com/article/011/0004258136?sid&#x3D;103\" class=\"se-oglink-info\" target=\"_blank\">\n                                    <div class=\"se-oglink-info-container\">\n                                        <strong class=\"se-oglink-title\">시험 때 마다, 고속버스 탈 때마다 배가 아프다고? &#x27;과민성 장 증후군&#x27;! [한방 원펀치]</strong>\n                                        <p class=\"se-oglink-summary\">“얘는 학교 가기 직전에 꼭 화장실에 가요. 매일 지각할까 봐 얼마나 걱정인지….” “고속버스 타기가 무서워요. 중간에 화장실 급해서 낭패 봤던 적이 많거든요. 그래서 차를 오래 타야 할 때면 미리 화장실을 들러야</p>\n                                        <p class=\"se-oglink-url\">n.news.naver.com</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module='{\"type\":\"v2_oglink\", \"id\" :\"SE-23680cf0-98db-4fbe-8d54-34691ab3728d\", \"data\" : {\"link\" : \"https://n.news.naver.com/article/011/0004258136?sid&#x3D;103\", \"isVideo\" : \"false\", \"thumbnail\" : \"https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src&#x3D;%22https%3A%2F%2Fimgnews.pstatic.net%2Fimage%2F011%2F2023%2F11%2F07%2F0004258136_001_20231107091405947.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw800%22&amp;type&#x3D;ff500_300\"}}